Astroblast finally nears the destination of the fight. All the robots
inside look out the front of the ship. &quot;Almost there. Remember the plan&quot;
says Motormaster. Just then a small yellow object comes into view, and gets
closer, and they can all hear a scream. The yellow race car bounces off
Astroblast, and transforms into Drag Strip as he hovers.

Astroblasts door opens, and Motormaster throws out the Squawktalk cassette.
